# Rediant Art Website - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
This is a bilingual (English/Russian) jewelry brand website for Rediant, featuring facechains, headchains, bodychains, and earrings. The site showcases 3D printing technology, crypto crowdfunding, and artistic jewelry design.

## File Structure
```
/
├── index.html (English homepage)
├── about.html (English about page)
├── collections.html (English collections)
├── 3d-printing.html (English 3D printing)
├── crowdfunding.html (English crowdfunding)
├── journal.html (English journal)
├── contact.html (English contact)
├── ru/ (Russian version folder)
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── about.html
│   ├── collections.html
│   ├── 3d-printing.html
│   ├── crowdfunding.html
│   ├── journal.html
│   └── contact.html
├── styles.css (Main stylesheet)
├── script.js (Main JavaScript)
├── Context/ (Content source files)
└── deploy.sh (Deployment script)
```

## Key Features
- **Bilingual Support**: Complete English and Russian versions
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach with breakpoints at 1024px, 768px, 480px
- **Language Switcher**: Integrated into navigation menu
- **3D Printing Focus**: Technology and innovation showcase
- **Crypto Crowdfunding**: Bitcoin-based funding system
- **SEO Optimized**: Meta tags, structured data, optimized keywords

## Design System
- **Colors**: 
  - Primary: #D4AF37 (gold)
  - Secondary: #2C2C2C (charcoal)
  - Accent: #F5F5F5 (warm neutral)
- **Typography**: 
  - Headings: Playfair Display (serif)
  - Body: Inter (sans-serif)
- **Spacing**: CSS custom properties for consistent spacing
- **Shadows**: Subtle shadows for depth

